songs.title: Love In Da Mall
songs.lyrics:
Yeah
TTDD y'all
Hot fire

[Chorus:]
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow

[Verse 1:]
Yeah
I saw you at the mall just the other day
I was walkin' you was walkin' the other way
I said girl
Come over here what's yo name, what's yo number
You hesitated to give me those seven digits
I said give me your number biznitch
Or we gon' have so muthafuckin' issues
I might have to hit you

[Chorus:]
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow
Ooh ooh oh
(Love in da mall)

I saw you later
At the movies lookin' good
[?]
After the movies we saw
Each other in the mall
I said hey chick
What's yo address
You gave me a stinky face
I said what's the deal bitch?
I got this pistol
Pow Pow
Leave you in the dust hoe
Yeh yeah yeh yeah yeah

[Bridge:]
I was (I was)
Walkin' at her (Walkin' at her)
[?]
That's when I (I)
I saw her
Feet (Look at that big toe)
Girl
(More incomprehensible sounds)
TTDD
One more time for me

[Chorus:]
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow
Ooh woo woo woo woo woo wow wow

Tyler, Taco, The bomb, Domo
Love in da mall
Uh yeah this to all dem bitches out there
{?]
With the EBT cards
Swag that shit out brotha

Taco begins screaming a mixture of the words: Odd, Future and .com
